column5: I am going to Lac Suel on June 10th thru June 19th. Have room for one person. I have a cabin rented and have been there for years. If interested contact me. Leaving from Minnesota.
Dang, I'm already going those same days with my wife. Maybe...........I better not.
Where are you staying at on Lac Seul and where in Minnesota are you leaving from?
staying at DeerPath Lodge by Hudson. Leavoing from Mankato, Minnesota. You can e-mail me if you wish. Just click on the icon in right side
Jimbo Two of us will arrive there on the 18th. Will probably need some spots to get started if you could help us. What cabin are you staying in ? Thanks, Tom
I think it is cabin 3. It is right straight ahead of the drive way going up the hill from fish cleaning house. I drive a Chev. Avalance with Alumacraft boat. Where you from???

We live near Madison, Wis. Went there for the first time last year. Huge area to scout out....that's why I could use the help. It was hit or miss for us last year, and the weather did not help. When we get there, any tips would be appreciated. Thanks again, Tom
